## Implementation Considerations

### Claude Integration Best Practices
- Provide meaningful context to Claude
- Include relevant file metadata 
- Use thinking mode for complex organization tasks
- Create clear prompts that define organization goals

### File Operations Safety
- Always confirm before moving/deleting files
- Implement undo functionality
- Log all file operations
- Handle permission errors gracefully

### GUI Design Principles
- Keep the interface simple and intuitive
- Provide clear feedback for long-running operations
- Include dark mode option (aligning with your preference)
- Include progress indicators for file operations

## Getting Started

To begin development:

